... RELEASE NOTES

It's been 10 years since we started DDS and although we
have been inactive for almost 7,5 of those 10 years,
it's still our anniversary :). Being able to still
bring quality, and compete with long-time friends and
groups,it's still good enough for us to stick around.
900+ releases in 10 years isn't really that much,
but considering our absence for 7,5 years it's still
a good average.
Keep enjoying our stuff, smoke a cigar while doing so
and smack your goddamn head on your keyboard when
shit hits the fan!

... GROUP iNFOS

DDS is here for fun only, we try to keep the scene
standard as high as possible. It's not difficult to
compete, but compete with quality is much harder.

Our releases will be here for your pleasure, and
for scene-pleasure only! So keep them off P2P!

... GREETiNGS

Greetings go out to all our friends in the scene

and the people who support us!
